    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generally, may refer to showy unsubstantial objects, especially a useless ornament. Specifically, typically refers to mechanical contrivances or scientific apparatuses that are collectible but of little utilitarian value. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Kan in algemene zin verwijzen naar opzichtige, goedkope voorwerpen, met name nutteloze ornamenten. In specifieke zin wordt met deze term ook verwezen naar mechanische uitvindingen of technische apparaten die alleen dienen als verzamelobject.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052403/Van Dale Groot Woordenboek (1998)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一般係指華而不實的物件，特別是無用的裝飾品。通常專指用來收藏，但不具實用價值的機械裝置或科學設備。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
